A 411/412 used a BA 4 heater, not a BN 4.
Totally different style and operating procedure.
The BA 4 sits on top of the transaxle. Here is a pic of it:
http://wow.atlasta.net/~mriluvu/oacdp/ebersp/009.png
And here it is the Type 4:
http://wow.atlasta.net/~mriluvu/oacdp/ebersp/005.png

The BN 4 sits in the left rear corner of the bus:
http://wow.atlasta.net/~mriluvu/oacdp/ebersp/037.png
